oji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: BeWaterHK"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5570da790006863b3b8118b06300ee323e65c1d4","tid":1501024,"uid":311113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"push 英文文宣組"},{"pid":"b8e4d5208152cb45b2038a1e6d58a8a0befdc763","tid":1501024,"uid":311113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a65d8c147104df40f87c61bccfc347241f2616a6","tid":1501024,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:10:11.000Z","msg":"During 24th August Kwun Tong Anti-Surveillance March, a smart lamp post has been taken down to express our rejection to surveillance. We found out that the parts inside were made in China, also it is from a company called Tickteck Technology. After further research, we discovered that Sansi Technology is Tickteck&rsquo;s mother company. The system has been logged in and confirmed that the data is sent to China as the location has been shown.<br />\nThe message we try to bring forward to the world now is that<br />\nEVERY COUNTRY THAT USED SURVEILLANCE SYSTEM MADE IN CHINA, <br />\nARE BEING WATCHED BY CHINA.<br />\nChina would receive all data collected by lamp post from countries including UK, Canada, Singapore, Spain and more.<br />\n<br />\n#ChiNAZI<br />\n#Chairman Xi is watching you<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLJgAPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLJgAPH.png&h=8a343c27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NewYO9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNewYO9H.png&h=f5a70fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tx0iO9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftx0iO9H.png&h=13fc4234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4ed1c1d723e49fa722996ed46d925ff8a04a4b8","tid":1501024,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"pp"},{"pid":"a6fdfa36ae3598fd7fec94ec89d775f681e13f22","tid":1501024,"uid":266396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:15:21.000Z","msg":"我幫你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b89b88ebfc0ba43def743a4f8f8ac049330938","tid":1501024,"uid":42103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fdfd9aaeed3a8ddcf67be2b6b9df25960d768f","tid":1501024,"uid":299984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:16:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1be227da3859b19a29c05a246cf552ab01796d2e","tid":1501024,"uid":235259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:17:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e09b5cd129871aa7be471e1d744dbaa738427a6d","tid":1501024,"uid":160166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"【國際戰線】同我like哂以下Twitter tag佢<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502002</a>"},{"pid":"5fc326eb00c3a88d40590c2ec5b4ff2e5564223c","tid":1501024,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f73a8032cd3dce27e18b83f1caccd84f440bea5","tid":1501024,"uid":57274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qzvrc0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzvrc0y.png&h=d84bb6b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;Smart lamp posts&rdquo; that has first built for trial in Kwun Tong and Kowloon Bay have raised big concerns of total Surveillance among HK citizens.<br />\n<br />\nThe smart lamp posts are equipped with 360&deg; camera, Radio Frequency IDentification(RFID), 5G Wireless internet etc.<br />\nThe general public is worried of face recognition and RFID function which put every citizens under surveillance. Although the government claimed that face recognition function is not yet available, TVB has once revealed this function in one of their programmes, Erasing the episode afterwards. Also citizens who have changed new HKID or used 5G network could be traced by the smart lamp posts.<br />\n<br />\nThe HK government has been trying to deny its surveillance function ever since which reveals the real evil goal. <br />\nToday, during Kwun Tong Anti- Surveillance March, a smart lamp post has fallen down in Kowloon Bay. <br />\nAS A FREE HONG KONG CITIZEN,<br />\nWE WOULD NEVER LET CHI NAZI TO IMPOSE TOTAL SURVEILLANCE IN HONG KONG<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, the revolution of our times.<br />\n<br />\nTVB&rsquo;s erased scene: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bqt4J64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqt4J64.png&h=855ddb38&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"有冇得做張精而簡既文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a8623f0966d9b167f38721c0500fcfc781254f","tid":1501024,"uid":221988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98204692891b481fb8554fd5b2c4e9ac48b1b45d","tid":1501024,"uid":221988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"838f011151ea5b0b5f9407b8d5709a8a3bed48b5","tid":1501024,"uid":221988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7670949fc60185399ff7efa8dad6ab0c75e0af39","tid":1501024,"uid":57433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:31:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\